title: House 101 (Architecture Art Ebook).pdf
description:
House 101 By George Lam
2008 | 224 Pages | ISBN: 9627723517 | PDF | 79 MB

This title features 40 new and significant house designs submitted by 40 architectural practices around the world including ODBC-Paris, Tonkin, Swatt Architects, Saia Barbarese Topouzanov, Paul Morgan Architects, Mark Dziewulski, K. Fujimoto Architect, Elmslie Osler Architect and bgp arquitectura. Each of these inspirational designs is richly illustrated with photographs and detailed plans
